About ggzdmod++
===============

From GGZ 0.0.12 on, ggzdmod++ provides the functionality of both ggzdmod
and the networking part of libggz to C++ game servers.

Classes
=======
Net: reading and writing of strings and numbers over the network
MNet: communication with a group of selected peers
GGZGameServer: player/spectator/bot handling, startup/shutdown, events

